A new {doc}`/backends/index` section provides a support matrix and
per-engine pages ({doc}`/backends/codex`, {doc}`/backends/claude`,
{doc}`/backends/cursor-cli`, {doc}`/backends/cursor-ide`,
{doc}`/backends/gemini`, {doc}`/backends/grok`) documenting store
layouts, adapter IDs, and record schemas.

